<ol sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="75">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="75"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="75">Change the country/region to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="75">POL</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="76"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="76">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="76">Ledger</strong> page, verify that the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="76">Accounting currency</strong> field is set to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="76">EUR</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">Set up currency exchange rates for the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">Default</strong> exchange rate type, as shown in the following table.</p>
