<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-pol-split-ap-ar-exchange-difference.md" sourcestartlinenumber="150">1.90 (= 11.90 – 10.00) is the exchange difference that is related to the tax amount of the invoice.</li>
</ul>
